subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Jiyai Shin of South Korea shot a seven-under-par 64, then beat Angela Stanford of the United States and Sun Young Yoo of South Korea on the second hole of a sudden-death playoff to win the P&G Beauty NW Arkansas Championship.
